-#79029 (Use After Free's in XMLReader / XMLWriter)
---SKIPIF--
-<?php if (!extension_loaded("xmlwriter")) print "skip"; ?>
---FILE--
-<?php
-$x = array( new XMLWriter() );
-$x[0]->openUri("a");
-$x[0]->startComment();
-?>
-okey
---EXPECT--
-okey
